## 📦 Datasets

### 🛒 Sales_Data_Ecommerce.csv
> 160,000 records · 18 columns · October 2019

This dataset captures individual user interaction events on an e-commerce platform, 
recording browsing and purchasing behaviour across **Browser** and **App** channels.
It includes product details such as category, brand and price, along with the user's US
State and an engagement score. This is the **primary dataset** driving the sales trends,
traffic patterns, and customer behaviour analysis.

---

### 🏷️ Promotion.csv.xlsx
> 61 records · 4 columns · October 2019

This dataset contains promotional campaign records, linking each unique promotion ID to a 
specific product, the date it was active, and the **discount percentage** offered. It is 
used alongside the sales data to evaluate how promotions influenced purchasing decisions 
and overall revenue performance.
